description:
Never wake me up from this Sicilian dream!🥹✨ Visiting Sicily has been a dream of mine, and it finally came true! Sicily is full of stunning towns and breathtaking spots, but we decided to stay in a small local gem called Castellammare del Golfo. I was inspired to visit after seeing my friend @annakatinkafehr post the most incredible pictures from her trip. We rented an adorable Airbnb (link below!) and highly recommend staying there. We spent a whole week in Sicily, relaxing on the beach, cooking delicious meals at home, exploring a ceramic market, and driving around to discover unique and beautiful places nearby. I hope this video inspires you to visit Sicily someday! Sending the biggest hugs your way xx

Link to the airbnb: https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/33905576?source_impression_id=p3_1726582372_P3EjuEksgVPgh0sL

places we visited:
The beach in Castellamare - Cala Petròlo
Pizza restaurant - Gusto Pizzeria Siculo Napoletana
Ice cream - Gelateria Vernaci
Ceramic market - SS187, 95 (Ceramica Fatima)
“Hidden beach” - Cala Bianca
Fishery, bathing area - Tonnara Di Scopello
Restaurant in Scopello - Ristorante La Terrazza
